# Four-in-a-Row (4x4 Tic-Tac-Toe)

## Description
This is a web-based implementation of a 4x4 "Four-in-a-Row" Tic-Tac-Toe game. Two players (the user and the computer) take turns placing “O” and “X” marks on a 4x4 board. The objective is to get four of the same symbol in a row—vertically, horizontally, or diagonally.


## How to Play

1. Clone and download the repository, or click codespace ide link
2. Open a terminal 
3. Install dependencies:
   npm install
4. Start the server: 
   node server.js
5. Open your browser:
   https://crispy-fortnight-px95jw4p7xpfx45-3000.app.github.dev/


## You can run and preview the game using codespace ide link: 
https://crispy-fortnight-px95jw4p7xpfx45.github.dev/

